page_title: Azure OpenAI on your Azure Cosmos DB data Python & REST API reference
page_description: Learn how to use Azure OpenAI on your Azure Cosmos DB data Python & REST API.
chunk_content: Endpoint vectorization sourceThe details of the vectorization source, used by Azure OpenAI On Your Data when applying vector search. This vectorization source is based on the Azure OpenAI embedding API endpoint.|Name | Type | Required | Description ||--- | --- | --- | --- || `endpoint`|string|True|Specifies the resource endpoint URL from which embeddings should be retrieved. It should be in the format of `https://{YOUR_RESOURCE_NAME}.openai.azure.com/openai/deployments/YOUR_DEPLOYMENT_NAME/embeddings`. The api-version query parameter isn't allowed.|| `authentication`| ApiKeyAuthenticationOptions|True | Specifies the authentication options to use when retrieving embeddings from the specified endpoint.|| `type`|string|True| Must be `endpoint`.|
